cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD 

This paper discusses the intersection of language origins research and emergent communication in computer science and machine learning. It specifically focuses on the target of compositionality and suggests an alternative approach of reflexivity. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SD (Sound).
